This paper discusses the strength of ties on Facebook, which is a social networking platform. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also touches upon the concept of community, which falls under cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences). Additionally, the paper discusses privacy and security concerns on Facebook, which could fall under cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity). The paper also mentions the use of algorithms to analyze Facebook data, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
